  <brief_title>A Study of ALKS 5461 for Treatment Refractory Major Depressive Disorder (MDD)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 3b Efficacy and Safety Study of Adjunctive ALKS 5461 in Treatment Refractory Major Depressive Disorder</official_title>
